	        <div class="commentcontent"><p>I have thrown huge parties with this recipe. No hang over!<br />
I used a 50 gallon bin.<br />
Throw in lots of chopped orange apples lemon. Add 2 lbs cane sugar<br />
Bottle of white rum, orange liqueur, brandy.<br />
Stir leave for 30 mins to ferment!!</p>
<p>Add 5 ltr sweet red from the bodega<br />
Plus 5ltr dry red<br />
Leave for 2 hours at least.<br />
Add huge block of ice as much as you like 10 ltr<br />
Pour two ltr sprite over the ice. More if you like.<br />
Stir<br />
Leave until serving. Up to you. About 45 mins.</p>
</div>

